       enforce it (e.g. flag a shadow in a borders-only system). -->
- **Surface scale:** {{SURFACE_SCALE}}   <!-- e.g. --surface-0 base · --surface-1 raised -->
- **Control tokens:** {{CONTROL_TOKENS}} <!-- --control-bg · --control-border · --control-focus -->

